  "docs": {
    "sections": [
      {
        "kind": "summary",
        "title": "Summary",
        "blocks": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "Difference (subtraction) of two polynomials."
          },
          {
            "type": "directive",
            "name": "note",
            "body": "   This forms part of the old polynomial API. Since version 1.4, the\n   new polynomial API defined in `numpy.polynomial` is preferred.\n   A summary of the differences can be found in the\n   :doc:`transition guide </reference/routines.polynomials>`.",
            "raw": ".. note::\n   This forms part of the old polynomial API. Since version 1.4, the\n   new polynomial API defined in `numpy.polynomial` is preferred.\n   A summary of the differences can be found in the\n   :doc:`transition guide </reference/routines.polynomials>`."
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "Given two polynomials `a1` and `a2`, returns ``a1 - a2``.\n`a1` and `a2` can be either array_like sequences of the polynomials'\ncoefficients (including coefficients equal to zero), or `poly1d` objects."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "kind": "parameters",
        "title": "Parameters",
        "items": [
          {
            "name": "a1, a2",
            "type": "array_like or poly1d",
            "desc_blocks": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Minuend and subtrahend polynomials, respectively."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "kind": "returns",
        "title": "Returns",
        "items": [
          {
            "name": "out",
            "type": "ndarray or poly1d",
            "desc_blocks": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Array or `poly1d` object of the difference polynomial's coefficients."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "kind": "examples",
        "title": "Examples",
        "blocks": [
